name: 219 Baltic Quay ( from the series)
description:
219 Baltic Quay, Newcastle Upon Tyne 
I've been living in this place for about 3 years right after my marriage. The view from the windows of this 2bedroom apartment was toward the Sage Gates-head where I used to go to singing classes once a week. Swing bridge and Tyne bridge are also painted in this illustration. The reflection of sunset was so inspirational and romantic that I couldn't resist but illustrating the scenery.
